data.description: Gorgeous 3-bedroom, 2-bath located in Lakewood Manor. This completely updated and remodeled home is bright, and modern; with an open living room, cozy fireplace, and newer flooring throughout. Open the sliding door, and you're in a welcoming yard perfect for enjoying California's weather. The newer upgraded kitchen, complete with an oversized countertop and bar, is perfect for both entertaining, and everyday living. Right next to the kitchen is a spacious laundry room with extra cabinets and lots of extra storage space. The primary suite includes a newly updated ensuite bath, while the two secondary bedrooms and another remodeled full bath are conveniently located across the hall. And don't overlook the versatile garage with epoxy floors and custom cabinets. This space is ideal for a bonus room, game room, home gym or whatever your heart desires.  Conveniently located near parks and shopping, with easy freeway access, this home is move-in ready!
